Six men were killed at the Jabulani hostel in Soweto and the police top brass wants answers. Police Minister Bheki Cele is visiting the scene. #eNCA Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Police are following up on leads regarding a mass murder at Jabulani Hostel in Soweto on Monday night. READ: Two traffic wardens gunned down in KZN Six men were fatally gunned down in their shack located inside the hostel precinct.  A seventh victim is recovering in hospital. Police are searching for three gunmen believed to be involved.